text: Illusive is the adjective form of illusory. Illusive may also refer to: * Illusive Islands, Nunavut, Canada * Illusive Sounds, an independent Australian hip hop record label * Illusive Tracks, a Swedish dark comedy thriller film * Snowflake/Illusive, a 7" vinyl picture disc single by Psychic TV * USS Illusive (AM-448), minesweeper ship * Illusive (album) ==See also== * Illusion
title: Illusive
